data.description: ***Ask about the possibility of receiving 1% reduction in interest rate and free refi.*** Welcome to your serene retreat in Walterboro! Nestled in a peaceful, wooded setting, this charming home invites you to embrace tranquility.As you head down the long driveway, the natural surroundings greet you, setting the tone for the beauty that lies ahead. Step onto the welcoming front porch and feel the stress of the day melt away.Enter into an inviting open floor plan, where lovely flooring and abundant natural light create an inviting ambiance. The formal dining room seamlessly transitions into the spacious family room, adorned with vaulted ceilings, a cozy fireplace, and doors leading out to the deck, offering views of the surrounding landscape. The functional kitchen boasts whitecabinets and updated stainless steel appliances, making meal preparation a breeze.  Retreat to the spacious owner's suite, complete with an en suite bath featuring a step-in shower, providing the perfect sanctuary after a long day. Two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient laundry room round out the living space. New light fixtures can be found in every bedroom.  For the handy homeowner, the garage includes a workshop area, perfect for tinkering on projects or storage.  Step outside onto the deck and immerse yourself in the tranquility of the backyard. The large screen porch beckons for relaxation with its light/fan and TV hook up, offering an ideal spot to soak in the natural beauty. The home is adjacent to the Walterboro Wildlife Sanctuary including the elaborate woodland trail system traversing the hardwood forest and numerous "braided" creeks.  Conveniently located just a few blocks from downtown Walterboro, this home combines the beauty of nature with the convenience of city living. Don't miss your opportunity to make this tranquil oasis your own. Schedule your showing today!
